content:
Boost your sales teams’ results with new features across Sales Cloud. 
Sales rep’s get a boost to their productivity with standard and custom list view actions in the Account, Contact, and Lead Intelligence views. 
Conversation Signals gives sales teams a bird's-eye view of conversations with customers. 
Generative Conversation Insights creates custom insights for video calls, answering questions like customer sentiment or deal terms. 
Sales managers have more flexibility in how they view forecasts. 

Einstein for Sales features include:
drafting sales emails from a sales rep’s inbox and including related information with generative AI
visualizing contacts in a relationship map to ramp up on accounts and opportunities
adding buyer profile data to contacts automatically to avoid manual data entry

Sales Foundations includes:
creating contacts automatically from email and calendar activity
applying personal labels to organize and find records
getting more information on the Seller Home page
boosting productivity with standard and custom list view actions in Account, Contact, and Lead Intelligence views.

Einstein Conversation Insights provides:
Conversation Signals for a bird's-eye view of conversations with customers
Generative Conversation Insights for creating custom insights powered by generative AI
processing single-user meetings
expanding edit access to record collections

Sales Engagement features include:
linking cadences
using screen flows as cadence steps
saving cadences in any folder
creating and editing email templates in Cadence Builder 2.0

Revenue Intelligence includes:
lead metrics in the Einstein Account Management Account Inspector
hourly app refresh schedule for updating revenue data more frequently
Resources tab for exploring Revenue Insights resources after a successful app installation

Collaborative Forecasts allow sales managers to review forecast rollups by team, then by forecast group or product family.

Pipeline Inspection boosts productivity with standard and custom list view actions in Pipeline Inspection. 

Sales Programs and Partner Tracks with Enablement includes:
immediate, actionable feedback on sales pitches courtesy of Einstein
creating programs that align with complex revenue metrics
providing transparency and accountability to users who take your programs

Partner Relationship Management helps partner sellers draft personalized emails quickly with an assist from Einstein generative AI.

Sales Performance Management features include:
boosted processing performance for plotting high-volume data in Salesforce Maps framework
centralizing company segmentation, territories, and quota targets in Sales Planning
determining compensation for reps based on effective territory assignment dates in Enterprise Territory Management
title: Boosting Sales Performance with Salesforce
